---
title: Nanna's Chicken & Honey-Roasted Veggies with Garlic Couscous & Lemon Mayo
description: Our popular Nan's special seasoning, with paprika, pepper, onion and garlic, instantly adds a rich, classic flavour to succulent chicken thigh. Add sweet, honey-roasted veggies and creamy mayo for a dish worth enjoying again and again.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-adeles-chicken-with-honey-roasted-veggies-garlic-couscous-84f083b7.jpg
